{"type": "article", "id": 2199, "title": "多功能墙面收纳组合", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-07T22:08:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 2, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 10, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052222513JHwC850eDMS79fQ.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">Wall-Mounted Organizers 是一款多功能又能美化墙面的收纳组合。设计灵感来源于隆起的衬衫口袋，</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">使得这款产品拥有圆弧外形，简单、圆鼓鼓的轮廓给人以亲切之感，滑动式托架既方便固定在墙上，也易于拿下来清理，提供 4 种尺寸、6 种颜色的选择，设计师 Simon Legald，定价 17.5 美元，</span><a href=\"http://www.normann-copenhagen.com/families/pocket\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里购买</a><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726134859QYh54aonsqdWB106.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.95625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726134900ajAsdiqJTKtySCOV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726134900v8EangpZz32qLobG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></span>\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}